  "body": "<p>Here's a continuation (at long last!) from <a href=\"https://www.amytangerine.com/blog/2012/09/australia-wrap-up\">this Spotlight wrap up post</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"3a-IMG_0778-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600584115083-W96NTJNVV2OMHIQICHT2/3a-IMG_0778-600x450.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"3b-IMG_0771-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600584115098-8D640BSZGSQW7H153ZJM/3b-IMG_0771-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3c-IMG_0787-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600584115796-3LHOG3PLROE8YG8Z4XIA/3c-IMG_0787-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3d-IMG_0795-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600584115885-RUCRHNDYF7HWWAWFBD5V/3d-IMG_0795-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3e-IMG_0801-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600584116821-3BMMZPS13XII4G47ZOW8/3e-IMG_0801-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3f-IMG_0813-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600584116595-QR01E0OG3JHOW3P43TYH/3f-IMG_0813-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3g-IMG_0820-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600584117341-EP5DUK8230TOW2CFSE55/3g-IMG_0820-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3h-IMG_0830-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600584117434-PFFZCMJX30ELELBOXDLU/3h-IMG_0830-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3i-IMG_0826-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600584118075-QOPT1CQJMGW7GJQLF4MT/3i-IMG_0826-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3j-IMG_0836-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600584118204-PT5BXCBPV7NTUALFMMLQ/3j-IMG_0836-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3k-IMG_0822-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600584118822-KYSIH1F0G37SUMC648DR/3k-IMG_0822-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Still love how Beth immediately documented the visit in her Project Life. Other bloggers include <a href=\"http://btsoi.blogspot.com/2012/08/meeting-amy-tan.html\">btsoi</a> and <a href=\"http://intheeyesofmoonie.blogspot.com.au/2012/09/amy-tan-in-caboolture.html\">Moonie</a> and <a href=\"http://captureandcreate.wordpress.com/2012/09/09/helloooooo-anyone-there/\">Mandy B</a>. There's nothing quite like meeting all these wonderful, creative folks in person. Thanks again American Crafts, Spotlight and everyone who was a part of this awesome experience! Truly blessed and grateful.</p>"
